                \item Built a reporting module including grouping, filtering and charts
                \item Adapted our services to use a PDF export system, AJAX uploads, last updated, AJAX instant invites, dynamic charts, Gantt charts and AJAX prorating
                \item Made a sales \& CRM (customer relationship management) module including invoicing, product inventory, leads \& opportunity tracking, taxes and multiple currency support
                \item Created a finance module that records
                  transactions, expenses and assets.
                \item Managed deployment to and maintenance of
                  dedicated servers and AWS EC2 instances.
                     

\end{itemize}
